WEBVTT

00:00:00.644 --> 00:00:02.420
I'm a professional troublemaker.

00:00:02.444 --> 00:00:03.809
(Laughter)

00:00:04.349 --> 00:00:09.229
As my job is to critique the world,

00:00:10.058 --> 00:00:13.245
the shoddy systems and the people
who refuse to do better,

00:00:13.991 --> 00:00:17.166
as a writer, as a speaker,
as a shady Nigerian --

00:00:17.190 --> 00:00:18.215
(Laughter)

00:00:18.239 --> 00:00:22.220
I feel like my purpose is to be this cat.

00:00:22.244 --> 00:00:24.395
(Laughter)

00:00:24.419 --> 00:00:27.075
I am the person
who is looking at other people,

00:00:27.099 --> 00:00:28.663
like, "I need you to fix it."

00:00:29.331 --> 00:00:30.486
That is me.